{"tid":1612720,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"十一前後，澳門幾個聲援香港的行動被瘋狂打壓","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T03:13:35.000Z","uid":168446,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca097b1ffae31bc54aa3ae50516c889ca0afba87","tid":1612720,"uid":168446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:34:10.000Z","msg":"香港千祈唔可以輸，一輸就變澳門，請各位香港人花少少睇睇澳門發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n澳門人雖然紅底佔大多數，但一直都有少部分有心人想搞聲援行動，無理由當世界各地都有人數眾多嘅聲援行動，偏偏最近嘅澳門就冇架嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 澳門終審法院染紅，唔批反警暴集會</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70976775_133585304666777_3616795069517922304_n.png?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_eui2=AeHxy5Ob0E7cdtQkYzpq7Fyi6kuYOIM8j-SuTCDBHldX_Z2YdKqj85_bERwWwltRNQ7s0LUBz7Jq5vWNrqRbxnBQ3vjGuLamGeEoxWgIlCBCWg&amp;_nc_oc=AQnTHVPmVyCge3RruUsrglMukyh5Y8RhaYRnt480G8WfRLD8rOAFL92seJ3jSoy4j9E&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=0480d4a4ef45abe2ac9fd2256be128d5&amp;oe=5E27B78F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70976775_133585304666777_3616795069517922304_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_eui2%3DAeHxy5Ob0E7cdtQkYzpq7Fyi6kuYOIM8j-SuTCDBHldX_Z2YdKqj85_bERwWwltRNQ7s0LUBz7Jq5vWNrqRbxnBQ3vjGuLamGeEoxWgIlCBCWg%26_nc_oc%3DAQnTHVPmVyCge3RruUsrglMukyh5Y8RhaYRnt480G8WfRLD8rOAFL92seJ3jSoy4j9E%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D0480d4a4ef45abe2ac9fd2256be128d5%26oe%3D5E27B78F&h=b1902564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本今個星期有個集會抗議香港警察使用不當武力，澳警唔批准，集會發起人向終審法院上訴，結果敗訴，法院用嘅理由係，香港仲未有機關證實黑警使用不當武力，所以係失實，同埋因為香港係高度自治，澳門唔可以搞集會干預香港內部事務，完全係痴鳩線。<br />\n<br />\n終審法院3個法官，有2個係北京大學法律系畢業，1個葡籍法官，結果係兩個中國法官判敗訴，葡國法官判上訴得直，二比一最後都係輸。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://aamacau.com/2019/09/30/%e5%8f%8d%e8%ad%a6%e6%9a%b4%e9%9b%86%e6%9c%83%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4-%e7%b5%82%e9%99%a2%e6%99%9a%e4%b8%8a%e5%85%ac%e4%bd%88%e5%88%a4%e6%b1%ba-%e8%a3%81%e5%ae%9a%e7%99%bc%e8%b5%b7%e4%ba%ba%e6%95%97%e8%a8%b4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2F2019%2F09%2F30%2F%25e5%258f%258d%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%259a%25b4%25e9%259b%2586%25e6%259c%2583%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4-%25e7%25b5%2582%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%2599%259a%25e4%25b8%258a%25e5%2585%25ac%25e4%25bd%2588%25e5%2588%25a4%25e6%25b1%25ba-%25e8%25a3%2581%25e5%25ae%259a%25e7%2599%25bc%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2595%2597%25e8%25a8%25b4%2F&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=64802ac8\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamacau.com/2019/09/30/%e5%8f%8d%e8%ad%a6%e6%9a%b4%e9%9b%86%e6%9c%83%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4-%e7%b5%82%e9%99%a2%e6%99%9a%e4%b8%8a%e5%85%ac%e4%bd%88%e5%88%a4%e6%b1%ba-%e8%a3%81%e5%ae%9a%e7%99%bc%e8%b5%b7%e4%ba%ba%e6%95%97%e8%a8%b4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 貼聲援香港街招被警察拉</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://aamacau.com/files/uploads/2019/10/aamacau-photo-191001_1001_1512-1080x809.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2Ffiles%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2Faamacau-photo-191001_1001_1512-1080x809.jpg&h=ca6d34ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有兩個廿幾歲後生仔喺澳門街頭貼＜港澳連枝，風雨扶持＞傳單，聲援香港同埋反對人面識別天眼，結果被警察搜身拘捕，除左罰錢，仲話涉嫌刑事毀壞，唔知最後會唔會告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 十一煙花著黑衫被白衫跟踪</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有另一個活動係喺睇十一煙花現場，著黑衫集合埋一齊，為老共贈慶，但去到現場被大批白衫人士跟踪同影大頭，嚴重到覺得人身安全將受威脅，只能選擇解散。前一日亦有人著黑衫喺現場就被警察查證。<br />\n<a href=\"https://aamacau.com/2019/10/02/%e7%a8%b1%e8%a2%ab%e7%99%bd%e8%a1%a3%e4%ba%ba%e5%a3%ab%e7%be%a4%e8%b5%b7%e8%b7%9f%e8%b9%a4%e6%83%a1%e6%84%8f%e6%8b%8d%e5%a4%a7%e9%a0%ad%e7%85%a7-8%e2%80%a719%e9%bb%98%e7%ab%99%e7%99%bc%e8%b5%b7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2F%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e7%2599%25bd%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e7%25be%25a4%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e8%25b7%259f%25e8%25b9%25a4%25e6%2583%25a1%25e6%2584%258f%25e6%258b%258d%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e7%2585%25a7-8%25e2%2580%25a719%25e9%25bb%2598%25e7%25ab%2599%25e7%2599%25bc%25e8%25b5%25b7%2F&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=7e3288e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamacau.com/2019/10/02/%e7%a8%b1%e8%a2%ab%e7%99%bd%e8%a1%a3%e4%ba%ba%e5%a3%ab%e7%be%a4%e8%b5%b7%e8%b7%9f%e8%b9%a4%e6%83%a1%e6%84%8f%e6%8b%8d%e5%a4%a7%e9%a0%ad%e7%85%a7-8%e2%80%a719%e9%bb%98%e7%ab%99%e7%99%bc%e8%b5%b7/</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門巴絲們叫我向大家say sorry，做唔到啲咩實質行動支持香港人。唯一做到只係舉牌影相放上網：<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70982510_133481368010504_7410529739225432064_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_eui2=AeEQNQWr5M-XAiP9Rp0mIEpgPPwQ2VnLjeXAU68H47Qm7skxbsW6oxtQCn-XxKnQG2IxWI3vaO0FvTII8snzluqshTQgpDEygqsiikp0x71pyw&amp;_nc_oc=AQnyT9IeUPYpr8kpEhkp1O5IjMqXhfqfT5i4WjbhwYmilcGVO6BTyJxY_SRC99ysSgQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=ab30e2fb69418bcf35a987756d363914&amp;oe=5DF44F74\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70982510_133481368010504_7410529739225432064_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_eui2%3DAeEQNQWr5M-XAiP9Rp0mIEpgPPwQ2VnLjeXAU68H47Qm7skxbsW6oxtQCn-XxKnQG2IxWI3vaO0FvTII8snzluqshTQgpDEygqsiikp0x71pyw%26_nc_oc%3DAQnyT9IeUPYpr8kpEhkp1O5IjMqXhfqfT5i4WjbhwYmilcGVO6BTyJxY_SRC99ysSgQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Dab30e2fb69418bcf35a987756d363914%26oe%3D5DF44F74&h=d184fb98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個相簿：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/macau.standwithHK/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=133478764677431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmacau.standwithHK%2Fphotos%2F%3Ftab%3Dalbum%26album_id%3D133478764677431&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=1b44f7fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/macau.standwithHK/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=133478764677431</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋今個星期仲有個蘋果訪問，講兩個澳門中學生搞連儂牆俾警察查證，同埋澳門記者全行被禁去香港採訪，都值得一睇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190930/60091061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60091061&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=6e1d7337\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60091061&h=8e818ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190930/60091061</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門已經變成一個貼海報可以當係勇武行為嘅地方，一國兩制係可以崩潰到咁架，香港人付出任何代價都唔可輸架，澳門人都要靠你地頂住！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，光復澳門，時代革命！<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"33dc95a28e26b37b116fbeb15ecedfac67901a9b","tid":1612720,"uid":163630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"澳門巴絲萬事小心, 自身安全都好重要"},{"pid":"d63a543b200a05fd3e46df006df2d17624caf755","tid":1612720,"uid":168446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:41:31.000Z","msg":"自推第一次"},{"pid":"266949ea008c27d2945639037395e7b53b3a32b3","tid":1612720,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n係時候推下實際行動 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611678</a>"},{"pid":"78e2e76f5dcb90c1db2848e6205fd4fe4b139ea9","tid":1612720,"uid":168446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:46:25.000Z","msg":"自推第二次"},{"pid":"c89e39ea9fe496ed46f9c2d74c03f38e82b513e7","tid":1612720,"uid":168446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:48:40.000Z","msg":"自推第三次"},{"pid":"27a470f33515b2b20c032809224d0a4c4828cf95","tid":1612720,"uid":75620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c3507513ab1e470e675b5ef45e92f6aa0f4944","tid":1612720,"uid":254191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"澳門同大陸已經冇分別<br />\n手足唔使行出黎聲援架"},{"pid":"601ebe429e0bd753ae8646a8f17d1407d407b54d","tid":1612720,"uid":75620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0c84850af352f5aace3523368b6cf04aa23354","tid":1612720,"uid":259725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}